{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There would be nothing to stop, and, and they kept us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They wanted to keep us, still, for exchange, although it was obviously ridiculous at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The train went on and on and on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and one night, we went to bed as usual-- and when I say bed, I mean we went to sleep in our-- we, we lay down on whatever we'd got left of our seats, because we'd used most of the wooden slats for cooking purposes.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But we lay down, maybe on the floor or something like that, like we did every other night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And when we woke up in the morning, the SS guards had gone, and outside we could see Russian soldiers on horses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we'd been liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was just like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There, there was no celebrations and there was no singing and, and nothing, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we didn't feel anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I say, we were just dumbfounded.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think we had any idea what it was like to be free, because we, we had been in camps and under domination by the Germans for such a long time that we just didn't appreciate what was happening.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So basically, first of all, we had to explain to the Russians who we were, because they saw this trainload full of people, kind of thing, with stars, admittedly, and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wondered what the hell was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we couldn't speak Russian to try and communicate to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't speak Dutch, which is what we all spoke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't want to speak German, because they were liable to just shoot Germans out of hand.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
